{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CMZCyYQR66hiCdLeLbNPfy","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* ============================================================\n     2→* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n     3→* ============================================================\n     4→* Subcircuit: ota_foldcasc\n     5→* Pins: vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n     6→*   vinp  = non-inverting input\n     7→*   vinn  = inverting input\n     8→*   vout  = output\n     9→*   vdd   = positive supply (1.8V)\n    10→*   vss   = ground\n    11→*   vbn   = NMOS current source bias (M9/M10/M11 gates)\n    12→*   vbcn  = NMOS cascode bias (M7/M8 gates)\n    13→*   vbp   = PMOS current source bias (M12/M13 gates)\n    14→*   vbcp  = PMOS cascode bias (M5/M6 gates)\n    15→* ============================================================\n    16→\n    17→* Parameterized device sizes for reusability\n    18→.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 1.0u  nf1  = 2\n    19→.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 1.0u  nf2  = 2\n    20→.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n    21→.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n    22→.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n    23→.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n    24→.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n    25→.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n    26→.param W9  =  4u   L9  = 2.0u  nf9  = 1\n    27→.param W10 =  4u   L10 = 2.0u  nf10 = 1\n    28→.param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1\n    29→.param W12 =  8u   L12 = 2.0u  nf12 = 1\n    30→.param W13 =  8u   L13 = 2.0u  nf13 = 1\n    31→\n    32→.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n    33→\n    34→* --- Input Differential Pair ---\n    35→* M1 (inp): drain=fold_p, gate=vinp, source=tail, body=vss\n    36→M1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W={W1} L={L1} nf={nf1}\n    37→* M2 (inn): drain=fold_n, gate=vinn, source=tail, body=vss\n    38→M2 fold_n vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W={W2} L={L2} nf={nf2}\n    