{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VqRwYzG4DVPrv18dCjGwQc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013aqueZDTAsHVyXatTewwfw","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice","content":"* ============================================================\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* ============================================================\n* Subcircuit: ota_foldcasc\n* Pins: vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n*   vinp  = non-inverting input\n*   vinn  = inverting input\n*   vout  = output\n*   vdd   = positive supply (1.8V)\n*   vss   = ground\n*   vbn   = NMOS current source bias (M9/M10/M11 gates)\n*   vbcn  = NMOS cascode bias (M7/M8 gates)\n*   vbp   = PMOS current source bias (M3/M4/M12/M13 gates)\n*   vbcp  = PMOS cascode bias (M5/M6 gates)\n* ============================================================\n*\n* Topology: Folded-cascode with NMOS input pair\n*\n*   VDD ── M12 ─┬─ M3 ── M5 ──┬── fold_p ── M7 ── M9 ── VSS\n*        (bias)  │  (fold)(pcasc)│          (ncasc) (csrc)\n*                │              │   M1 drain\n*                │              │\n*   VDD ── M13 ─┬─ M4 ── M6 ──┬── vout ──── M8 ── M10 ── VSS\n*        (bias)  │  (fold)(pcasc)│          (ncasc) (csrc)\n*                │              │   M2 drain\n*\n*   M11 (tail) connects M1/M2 sources to VSS\n*\n* M12/M13 form self-cascode with M3/M4 (shared Vbp gate)\n* for higher PMOS output impedance.\n* ============================================================\n\n* Parameterized device sizes for reusability\n.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 1.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 1.0u  nf2  = 2\n.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n.param W9  =  4u  