{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01MNr1mwf3DYU9pMXXtXSmt3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01NoMSDF6mAfmMTXsVwfzvXA","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/optimize_bias.spice","content":"* Bias optimization: sweep Vbcp with unity-gain feedback\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\nVss vss 0 dc 0\n\n* Bias: diode-connected NMOS for Vbn\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc 500n\n\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\n\n* PMOS bias: diode-connected\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\n\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\n\n* Unity-gain feedback\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\nRfb vout vinn 1\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.op\n\n.control\n  * Sweep Vbcp\n  foreach vbcp_val 0.60 0.65 0.70 0.75 0.80 0.85 0.90 0.95 1.00 1.05 1.10\n    alter Vbcp dc = $vbcp_val\n    op\n    echo \"Vbcp=$vbcp_val Vout=$&v(vout) M6_Vds=$&@m.xota.m6[vds] M4_Vds=$&@m.xota.m4[vds] M8_Vds=$&@m.xota.m8[vds]\"\n  end\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"Now sweep Vbcn with Vbcp=0.70:\"\n  alter Vbcp dc = 0.70\n  foreach vbcn_val 0.60 0.65 0.70 0.75 0.80 0.85 0.90 0.95 1.00\n    alter Vbcn dc = $vbcn_val\n    op\n    echo \"Vbcn=$vbcn_val Vout=$&v(vout) M8_Vds=$&@m.xota.m8[vds] M10_Vds=$&@m.xota.m10[vds] M7_Vds=$&@m.xota.m7[vds]\"\n  end\n\n  quit\n.endc\n\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5970,"cache_read_input_tokens":218087,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5970},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"dca1fe41-70