{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_0171rovhhH2HgUQYBubsCetC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014tUADQzqKegTVVCBHWFmow","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/find_bias.spice","content":"* Find optimal bias: sweep Vbp with ideal source, Vbcp with ideal source\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVss vss 0 dc 0\n\n* All ideal voltage sources for maximum control\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.58\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.83\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.85\n\n* Unity-gain feedback\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\nRfb vout vinn 1\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.op\n\n.control\n  * First, find Vbn that gives M11 = 500nA\n  echo \"=== Sweep Vbn ===\"\n  alter Vbp dc = 0.83\n  alter Vbcp dc = 0.85\n  foreach vbn_val 0.50 0.52 0.54 0.56 0.58 0.60 0.62 0.64 0.66 0.68 0.70\n    alter Vbn dc = $vbn_val\n    op\n    echo \"Vbn=$vbn_val M11=$&@m.xota.m11[id] M9=$&@m.xota.m9[id] Vout=$&v(vout)\"\n  end\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"=== Sweep Vbp with Vbn=0.58 ===\"\n  alter Vbn dc = 0.58\n  foreach vbp_val 0.76 0.78 0.80 0.82 0.84 0.845 0.850 0.855 0.860 0.865 0.870 0.88 0.90\n    alter Vbp dc = $vbp_val\n    op\n    echo \"Vbp=$vbp_val Vout=$&v(vout) M3=$&@m.xota.m3[id] M4=$&@m.xota.m4[id] M4_Vds=$&@m.xota.m4[vds] M6_Vds=$&@m.xota.m6[vds]\"\n  end\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"=== Sweep Vbcp with Vbn=0.58 Vbp=0.855 ===\"\n  alter Vbn dc = 0.58\n  alter Vbp dc = 0.855\n  foreach vbcp_val 0.60 0.65 0.70 0.75 0.80 0.82 0.84 0.86 0.88 0.90 0.92 0.94 0.96\n    alter Vbcp dc = $vbcp_val\n    op\n    echo \"Vbcp=$vbcp_val Vout=$&v(vout) M4_Vds=$&@m.xota.m4[vds] M6_Vds=$&@m.xota.m6[vds] M8_Vds=$&@m.xota.m8[vds] M10_Vds=$&@m.xota.m10[vds]\"\n  end\n\n  quit\n.endc\n\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2028,"cache_read_input_tokens":232158,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2028},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"90cf4dc1-85b4-4811-ad36-1361fb891837"}
