{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01JZSQrdydmg8nJF3cjzf2JB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"With 1T inductor:- The gain at low frequencies (100Hz - 1kHz) is about 14 dB- MAX gain is 56.2 dB (but this is the peak, likely from inductor resonance)- UGB = 30 kHz, PM = 178.6°\n\nThe gain is still weird — 14 dB at 100Hz-1kHz with a peak at 56 dB. The peak at 56 dB is from the inductor resonance with the OTA's output capacitance.\n\nThe actual open-loop DC gain should be visible in the flat region. \n\nAt 0.1 Hz, the inductor impedance is extremely high, yet the gain sits near unity at -0.27 dB because the inductor acts as a short at DC, allowing current to flow freely. As frequency increases toward 0.1 Hz, the impedance starts rising but hasn't fully blocked the signal yet.\n\nThe feedback path through the inductor remains active across the frequency range I'm examining. At low frequencies, the closed-loop gain hovers around 0 dB due to strong feedback (the loop gain T = A × β is high when β ≈ 1 through the inductor). As frequency climbs and the inductor impedance grows, feedback weakens and the gain rises. The relatively flat response at 100 Hz and 1 kHz—both around 14 dB—suggests the open-loop gain is only about 5x, which seems surprisingly low for this circuit.\n\nNow I'm noticing the UGB sits at 30 kHz while the gain at 10 kHz is 8.4 dB (roughly 2.6x), which fits a single-pole response with a 14 dB gain and pole around 10 kHz. Working backward from that 14 dB gain with the given transconductance, the output resistance comes out to about 833 kOhm—far too low for a folded cascode and more typical of a simple common-source stage. The operating point itself must be off, so I need to recheck it with the inductor in place since that's what sets the DC bias.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":358,"cache_read_input_tokens":262593,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":358},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"6b51521e-6472-49e0-9c5b-bce01f211e54"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01JZSQrdydmg8nJF3cjzf2JB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01PmY4uN2DQvutCDM4783TyU","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# Check OP with the inductor feedback (DC: vinn=vout)\ncat > op_check.spice << 'EOF'\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVss vss 0 dc 0\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc 500n\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\n\n* DC: inductor is short → vinn=vout\nLfb vout vinn 1T\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.op\n.control\n  run\n  echo \"Vout=$&v(vout) Vinn=$&v(vinn)\"\n  echo \"M1: Id=$&@m.xota.m1[id] Vds=$&@m.xota.m1[vds] gm=$&@m.xota.m1[gm]\"\n  echo \"M2: Id=$&@m.xota.m2[id] Vds=$&@m.xota.m2[vds] gm=$&@m.xota.m2[gm]\"\n  echo \"M4: Id=$&@m.xota.m4[id] Vds=$&@m.xota.m4[vds] Vdsat=$&@m.xota.m4[vdsat] gds=$&@m.xota.m4[gds]\"\n  echo \"M6: Id=$&@m.xota.m6[id] Vds=$&@m.xota.m6[vds] Vdsat=$&@m.xota.m6[vdsat] gm=$&@m.xota.m6[gm] gds=$&@m.xota.m6[gds]\"\n  echo \"M8: Id=$&@m.xota.m8[id] Vds=$&@m.xota.m8[vds] gm=$&@m.xota.m8[gm] gds=$&@m.xota.m8[gds]\"\n  echo \"M10: Id=$&@m.xota.m10[id] Vds=$&@m.xota.m10[vds] gds=$&@m.xota.m10[gds]\"\n  echo \"M11: Id=$&@m.xota.m11[id]\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"Estimated Rout_p = gm6*ro6*ro4 = $&@m.xota.m6[gm] * (1/$&@m.xota.m6[gds]) * (1/$&@m.xota.m4[gds])\"\n  echo \"Estimated Rout_n = gm8*ro8*ro10 = $&@m.xota.m8[gm] * (1/$&@m.xota.m8[gds]) * (1/$&@m.xota.m10[gds])\"\n  quit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\n/usr/bin/ngspice -b op_check.spice 2>&1 | grep -E \"^(Vout|M[0-9]|Estim)\" | head -15","description":"Check OP with inductor and Vbcp=0.70","timeout":60000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":358,"cache_read_input_tokens":262593,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":358},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"18017bb5-c20a-465c-827d-62b3c154ccbe"}
