{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01KQhdg7b7Tq5CYNPLM26Erc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The operating point is excellent now — M4_Vds=0.165V (saturation!). The expected gain is ~74 dB. The inductor feedback was distorting the AC measurement. Let me use `.tf` analysis for accurate DC gain."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2158,"cache_read_input_tokens":262951,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2158},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"d88c32ff-3f3b-4b27-9be2-6640248cd668"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01KQhdg7b7Tq5CYNPLM26Erc","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_012yLMTMTmwWLLUKCvaTt3RW","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > tf_check.spice << 'EOF'\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVss vss 0 dc 0\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc 500n\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\n\n* Unity-gain feedback at DC (inductor)\nLfb vout vinn 1T\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n* Transfer function from Vinp to v(vout)\n.tf v(vout) Vinp\n\n.control\n  run\n  print all\n  quit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\n/usr/bin/ngspice -b tf_check.spice 2>&1 | grep -E \"(transfer|output_imp|input_imp|v\\(vout\\))\" | grep -v \"Warning\" | head -10","description":"Measure DC transfer function","timeout":60000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2158,"cache_read_input_tokens":262951,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2158},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"b0b7ec9b-9fa4-4841-82b8-03705be2ee44"}
