{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01L7Ybsm4sSMXaBhhSqU5vxG","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"d4d14ae5-90e0-45e1-b599-8a1392b4bee6","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:49:09.158Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice","oldString":".param W1  = 10u   L1  = 1.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 1.0u  nf2  = 2","newString":".param W1  = 10u   L1  = 2.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 2.0u  nf2  = 2","originalFile":"* ============================================================\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* ============================================================\n* Subcircuit: ota_foldcasc\n* Uses raw BSIM4 model names (M-prefix, no subcircuit wrapper)\n* ============================================================\n\n* Parameterized device sizes for reusability\n.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 1.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 1.0u  nf2  = 2\n.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n.param W9  =  2u   L9  = 4.0u  nf9  = 1\n.param W10 =  2u   L10 = 4.0u  nf10 = 1\n.param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1\n.param W12 =  0.42u  L12 = 4.0u  nf12 = 1\n.param W13 =  0.42u  L13 = 4.0u  nf13 = 1\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input Differential Pair ---\nM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W1} L={L1} nf={nf1}\nM2 vout   vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W2} L={L2} nf={nf2}\n\n* --- Tail Current Source ---\nM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W11} L={L11} nf={nf11}\n\n* --- PMOS Fold Transistors (current sources from VDD) ---\nM3  mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W3} L={L3} nf={nf3}\nM4  mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W4} L={L4} nf={nf4}\n\n* --- PMOS Bias Mirror Transistors (parallel with M3/M4) ---\nM12 mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W12} L={L12} nf={nf12}\nM13 mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W13} L={L13} nf={nf13}\n\n* --- PMOS Cascode Transistors ---\nM5  fold_p vbcp mid_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W5} L={L5} nf={nf5}\nM6  vout   vbcp mid_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W6} L={L6} nf={nf6}\n\n* --- NMOS Cascode Transistors ---\nM7  fold_p vbcn src_n7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W7} L={L7} nf={nf7}\nM8  vout   vbcn src_n8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W8} L={L8} nf={nf8}\n\n* --- NMOS Current Source Transistors ---\nM9  src_n7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W9} L={L9} nf={nf9}\nM10 src_n8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W10} L={L10} nf={nf10}\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":6,"oldLines":8,"newStart":6,"newLines":8,"lines":[" * ============================================================"," "," * Parameterized device sizes for reusability","-.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 1.0u  nf1  = 2","-.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 1.0u  nf2  = 2","+.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 2.0u  nf1  = 2","+.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 2.0u  nf2  = 2"," .param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2"," .param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2"," .param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01GbNtq2faZ3EDNFxnmQwxFR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_019x2BTYgQQgS6uDc3Kib2tN","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# Quick check: OP + gain estimate with M1/M2 L=2u\ncat > quick_check.spice << 'EOF'\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVss vss 0 dc 0\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc 500n\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\nLfb vout vinn 1T\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.tf v(vout) Vinp\n\n.control\n  run\n  print transfer_function output_impedance_at_v(vout)\n  echo \"Gain = $&transfer_function\"\n  echo \"Rout_cl = $&output_impedance_at_v(vout)\"\n  \n  * Compute open-loop gain from closed-loop\n  * CL gain = A/(1+A), CL Rout = Rout_OL/(1+A)\n  * A = CL_gain/(1-CL_gain)\n  let cl_gain = transfer_function\n  let A = cl_gain / (1 - cl_gain)\n  let gain_db_est = 20*log(abs(A))/log(10)\n  echo \"Estimated OL Gain = $&A\"\n  echo \"Estimated OL Gain (dB) = $&gain_db_est\"\n  \n  * Also get device params\n  op\n  echo \"M2 gds=$&@m.xota.m2[gds] gm=$&@m.xota.m2[gm] Id=$&@m.xota.m2[id]\"\n  echo \"M4 Vds=$&@m.xota.m4[vds] Vdsat=$&@m.xota.m4[vdsat]\"\n  echo \"M6 Vds=$&@m.xota.m6[vds] M8 Vds=$&@m.xota.m8[vds]\"\n  echo \"Vout=$&v(vout)\"\n  quit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\n/usr/bin/ngspice -b quick_check.spice 2>&1 | grep -E \"^(Gain|Rout|Estim|M[0-9]|Vout|transfer|output)\" | head -15","description":"Quick check with L=2u input pair","timeout":60000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2828,"cache_read_input_tokens":268586,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2828},"output_tokens":36,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"a35837c3-e8f1-429e-8e1e-4e45a5fefe5c"}
