{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BzQ6x4Uq7MoTHMCv1KbHFk","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"d1942814-569d-4f67-9250-836ccb02d13e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:50:54.602Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice","oldString":".param W1  = 10u   L1  = 2.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 2.0u  nf2  = 2","newString":".param W1  = 20u   L1  = 4.0u  nf1  = 4\n.param W2  = 20u   L2  = 4.0u  nf2  = 4","originalFile":"* ============================================================\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* ============================================================\n* Subcircuit: ota_foldcasc\n* Uses raw BSIM4 model names (M-prefix, no subcircuit wrapper)\n* ============================================================\n\n* Parameterized device sizes for reusability\n.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 2.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 2.0u  nf2  = 2\n.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n.param W9  =  2u   L9  = 4.0u  nf9  = 1\n.param W10 =  2u   L10 = 4.0u  nf10 = 1\n.param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1\n.param W12 =  0.42u  L12 = 4.0u  nf12 = 1\n.param W13 =  0.42u  L13 = 4.0u  nf13 = 1\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input Differential Pair ---\nM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W1} L={L1} nf={nf1}\nM2 vout   vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W2} L={L2} nf={nf2}\n\n* --- Tail Current Source ---\nM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W11} L={L11} nf={nf11}\n\n* --- PMOS Fold Transistors (current sources from VDD) ---\nM3  mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W3} L={L3} nf={nf3}\nM4  mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W4} L={L4} nf={nf4}\n\n* --- PMOS Bias Mirror Transistors (parallel with M3/M4) ---\nM12 mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W12} L={L12} nf={nf12}\nM13 mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W13} L={L13} nf={nf13}\n\n* --- PMOS Cascode Transistors ---\nM5  fold_p vbcp mid_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W5} L={L5} nf={nf5}\nM6  vout   vbcp mid_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W6} L={L6} nf={nf6}\n\n* --- NMOS Cascode Transistors ---\nM7  fold_p vbcn src_n7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W7} L={L7} nf={nf7}\nM8  vout   vbcn src_n8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W8} L={L8} nf={nf8}\n\n* --- NMOS Current Source Transistors ---\nM9  src_n7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W9} L={L9} nf={nf9}\nM10 src_n8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W10} L={L10} nf={nf10}\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":6,"oldLines":8,"newStart":6,"newLines":8,"lines":[" * ============================================================"," "," * Parameterized device sizes for reusability","-.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 2.0u  nf1  = 2","-.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 2.0u  nf2  = 2","+.param W1  = 20u   L1  = 4.0u  nf1  = 4","+.param W2  = 20u   L2  = 4.0u  nf2  = 4"," .param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2"," .param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2"," .param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
