{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01BXXrQddT2whMcDKUTqrYtj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01SoUf6NRorFGVUFK49M3dWL","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# Run the proven configuration with AC measurement  \n# Use the 1T inductor approach and extract the peak gain\ncat > tb_ota_ac.spice << 'EOF'\n* AC Analysis - VibroSense OTA\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVss vss 0 dc 0\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc 500n\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\n\nVcm cm 0 dc 0.9\nVac vinp cm dc 0 ac 1\n\n* DC feedback via inductor\nLfb vout vinn 1T\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n* Start from very low frequency to see full response\n.ac dec 100 0.001 100Meg\n\n.control\n  run\n\n  * Find the peak gain (this approximates the DC open-loop gain)\n  meas ac gain_peak MAX vdb(vout)\n  \n  * UGB\n  meas ac ugb WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n  \n  * Phase at UGB\n  meas ac phase_ugb FIND vp(vout) AT=ugb\n  let pm = phase_ugb + 180\n\n  * Spot gains\n  meas ac g001 FIND vdb(vout) AT=0.01\n  meas ac g01 FIND vdb(vout) AT=0.1\n  meas ac g1 FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n  meas ac g10 FIND vdb(vout) AT=10\n  meas ac g100 FIND vdb(vout) AT=100\n  meas ac g1k FIND vdb(vout) AT=1000\n  meas ac g10k FIND vdb(vout) AT=10000\n  meas ac g100k FIND vdb(vout) AT=100000\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n  echo \"  AC Results\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n  echo \"Peak Gain: $&gain_peak dB\"\n  echo \"UGB: $&ugb Hz\"\n  echo \"Phase Margin: $&pm deg\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"Bode plot:\"\n  echo \"  0.01 Hz: $&g001 dB\"\n  echo \"  0.1 Hz:  $&g01 dB\"\n  echo \"  1 Hz:    $&g1 dB\"\n  echo \"  10 Hz:   $&g10 dB\"\n  echo \"  100 Hz:  $&g100 dB\"\n  echo \"  1 kHz:   $&g1k dB\"\n  echo \"  10 kHz:  $&g10k dB\"\n  echo \"  100 kHz: $&g100k dB\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n\n  wrdata bode_data vdb(vout) vp(vout)\n  quit\n.endc\n.end\nEOF\n/usr/bin/ngspice -b tb_ota_ac.spice 2>&1 | grep -E \"(Peak|UGB|Phase Mar|Bode|Hz:)\" | head -15","description":"Run comprehensive AC analysis","timeout":120000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2031,"cache_read_input_tokens":298786,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2031},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"e3875127-06e8-47b8-a2bf-1ec16d109613"}
