{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VtwJN6mXSb835egCXyucqT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Peak Gain = 60.0 dB, UGB = 26.0 kHz, PM = 178.5°**\n\nExcellent progress! The gain went from 31 dB to 60 dB with the longer M1/M2 (L=4u). The gain at 100Hz-1kHz (25 dB) is in the transition region of the inductor method — the true open-loop DC gain is the peak at 60 dB.\n\nWe're 5 dB short of the 65 dB target. Let me also increase the NMOS/PMOS cascode L to boost their contribution. And the UGB is slightly below the 30 kHz minimum — need to verify.\n\nLet me now try increasing M7/M8 L from 0.5u to 1u (doubles their ro, boosting NMOS cascode impedance) and M5/M6 L from 0.5u to 1u:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2759,"cache_read_input_tokens":300817,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2759},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"2a109ebd-ec9b-43c0-8fa1-85e7c4bde659"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VtwJN6mXSb835egCXyucqT","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01EGq9wy7T3WQDkYCTCA1igd","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice","old_string":".param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2","new_string":".param W5  =  8u   L5  = 1.0u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 1.0u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 1.0u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 1.0u  nf8  = 2"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2759,"cache_read_input_tokens":300817,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2759},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"9a487070-91b2-4cd5-b9d7-92644a95a3b2"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01EGq9wy7T3WQDkYCTCA1igd","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"944c308c-1b8d-4acb-822d-635c8a6708e2","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:58:14.158Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice","oldString":".param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2","newString":".param W5  =  8u   L5  = 1.0u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 1.0u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 1.0u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 1.0u  nf8  = 2","originalFile":"* ============================================================\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* ============================================================\n* Uses raw BSIM4 model names (M-prefix, no subcircuit wrapper)\n* Optimized for gain: M1/M2 L=4u for higher ro\n* M9/M10 W=2u L=4u for 0.5:1 mirror ratio\n* M12/M13 minimized (W=0.42u L=4u)\n* ============================================================\n\n.param W1  = 20u   L1  = 4.0u  nf1  = 4\n.param W2  = 20u   L2  = 4.0u  nf2  = 4\n.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n.param W9  =  2u   L9  = 4.0u  nf9  = 1\n.param W10 =  2u   L10 = 4.0u  nf10 = 1\n.param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1\n.param W12 =  0.42u  L12 = 4.0u  nf12 = 1\n.param W13 =  0.42u  L13 = 4.0u  nf13 = 1\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input Differential Pair (long L for high ro) ---\nM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W1} L={L1} nf={nf1}\nM2 vout   vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W2} L={L2} nf={nf2}\n\n* --- Tail Current Source ---\nM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W11} L={L11} nf={nf11}\n\n* --- PMOS Fold Transistors ---\nM3  mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W3} L={L3} nf={nf3}\nM4  mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W4} L={L4} nf={nf4}\n\n* --- PMOS Bias Mirror (minimized) ---\nM12 mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W12} L={L12} nf={nf12}\nM13 mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W13} L={L13} nf={nf13}\n\n* --- PMOS Cascode ---\nM5  fold_p vbcp mid_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W5} L={L5} nf={nf5}\nM6  vout   vbcp mid_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W6} L={L6} nf={nf6}\n\n* --- NMOS Cascode ---\nM7  fold_p vbcn src_n7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W7} L={L7} nf={nf7}\nM8  vout   vbcn src_n8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W8} L={L8} nf={nf8}\n\n* --- NMOS Current Source ---\nM9  src_n7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W9} L={L9} nf={nf9}\nM10 src_n8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W10} L={L10} nf={nf10}\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":11,"oldLines":10,"newStart":11,"newLines":10,"lines":[" .param W2  = 20u   L2  = 4.0u  nf2  = 4"," .param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2"," .param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2","-.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2","-.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2","-.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2","-.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2","+.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 1.0u  nf5  = 2","+.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 1.0u  nf6  = 2","+.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 1.0u  nf7  = 2","+.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 1.0u  nf8  = 2"," .param W9  =  2u   L9  = 4.0u  nf9  = 1"," .param W10 =  2u   L10 = 4.0u  nf10 = 1"," .param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
