- .ac dec 100 1 100Meg\n   - Measure common-mode gain, CMRR = diff_gain - cm_gain\n\nWrite all 6 files. DO NOT modify program.md, specs.json, requirements.md, or ota_foldcasc.spice.","uuid":"5717c187-7bcd-462e-9c3b-c668a2328019","session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d"}
