{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01BjEk2yH3GRG78hapFgUyDi","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* AC Analysis - VibroSense OTA\n     2→.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n     3→.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n     4→\n     5→Vdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\n     6→Vss vss 0 dc 0\n     7→Mbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\n     8→Ibias vdd vbn dc 500n\n     9→Vbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\n    10→Mbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\n    11→Ibp vbp 0 dc 500n\n    12→Vbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\n    13→\n    14→Vcm cm 0 dc 0.9\n    15→Vac vinp cm dc 0 ac 1\n    16→\n    17→* DC feedback via inductor\n    18→Lfb vout vinn 1T\n    19→\n    20→Xota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\n    21→CL vout 0 10p\n    22→\n    23→* Start from very low frequency to see full response\n    24→.ac dec 100 0.001 100Meg\n    25→\n    26→.control\n    27→  run\n    28→\n    29→  * Find the peak gain (this approximates the DC open-loop gain)\n    30→  meas ac gain_peak MAX vdb(vout)\n    31→  \n    32→  * UGB\n    33→  meas ac ugb WHEN vdb(vout)=0 FALL=1\n    34→  \n    35→  * Phase at UGB\n    36→  meas ac phase_ugb FIND vp(vout) AT=ugb\n    37→  let pm = phase_ugb + 180\n    38→\n    39→  * Spot gains\n    40→  meas ac g001 FIND vdb(vout) AT=0.01\n    41→  meas ac g01 FIND vdb(vout) AT=0.1\n    42→  meas ac g1 FIND vdb(vout) AT=1\n    43→  meas ac g10 FIND vdb(vout) AT=10\n    44→  meas ac g100 FIND vdb(vout) AT=100\n    45→  meas ac g1k FIND vdb(vout) AT=1000\n    46→  meas ac g10k FIND vdb(vout) AT=10000\n    47→  meas ac g100k FIND vdb(vout) AT=100000\n    48→\n    49→  echo \"\"\n    50→  echo \"======================================================\"\n    51→  echo \"  AC Results\"\n    52→  echo \"======================================================\"\n    53→  echo \"Peak Gain: $&gain_peak dB\"\n    54→  echo \"UGB: $&ugb Hz\"\n    55→  echo \"Phase Margin: $&pm deg\"\n    56→  echo \"\"\n    57→  echo \"Bode plot:\"\n    58→  echo \"  0.01 Hz: $&g001 dB\"\n    59→  echo \"  0.1 Hz:  $&g01 dB\"\n    60→  echo \"  1 Hz:    $&g1 dB\"\n    61→  echo \"  10 Hz:   $&g10 dB\"\n    62→  echo \"  100 Hz:  $&g100 dB\"\n    63→  echo \"  1 kHz:   $&g1k dB\"\n    64→  echo \"  10 kHz:  $&g10k dB\"\n    65→  echo \"  100 kHz: $&g100k dB\"\n    66→  echo \"======================================================\"\n    67→\n    68→  wrdata bode_data vdb(vout) vp(vout)\n    69→  quit\n    70→.endc\n    71→.end\n    72→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01EZLvWR7y8upt6isXr71TxJ","session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"33e056a2-16a6-4118-8f9e-7ea4e1ceaa26","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:01:12.592Z"}
