{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Gk7dw3BEBWY9VxYQrDLjZA","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* ============================================================\n     2→* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n     3→* ============================================================\n     4→* Uses raw BSIM4 model names (M-prefix, no subcircuit wrapper)\n     5→* Optimized for gain: M1/M2 L=4u for higher ro\n     6→* M9/M10 W=2u L=4u for 0.5:1 mirror ratio\n     7→* M12/M13 minimized (W=0.42u L=4u)\n     8→* ============================================================\n     9→\n    10→.param W1  = 80u   L1  = 16.0u  nf1  = 8\n    11→.param W2  = 80u   L2  = 16.0u  nf2  = 8\n    12→.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n    13→.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n    14→.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n    15→.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n    16→.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n    17→.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n    18→.param W9  =  2u   L9  = 4.0u  nf9  = 1\n    19→.param W10 =  2u   L10 = 4.0u  nf10 = 1\n    20→.param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1\n    21→.param W12 =  0.42u  L12 = 4.0u  nf12 = 1\n    22→.param W13 =  0.42u  L13 = 4.0u  nf13 = 1\n    23→\n    24→.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n    25→\n    26→* --- Input Differential Pair (long L for high ro) ---\n    27→M1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W1} L={L1} nf={nf1}\n    28→M2 vout   vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W2} L={L2} nf={nf2}\n    29→\n    30→* --- Tail Current Source ---\n    31→M11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W11} L={L11} nf={nf11}\n    32→\n    33→* --- PMOS Fold Transistors ---\n    34→M3  mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W3} L={L3} nf={nf3}\n    35→M4  mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W4} L={L4} nf={nf4}\n    36→\n    37→* --- PMOS Bias Mirror (minimized) ---\n    38→M12 mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W12} L={L12} nf={nf12}\n    39→M13 mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W13} L={L13} nf={nf13}\n    40→\n    41→* --- PMOS Cascode ---\n    42→M5  fold_p vbcp mid_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W5} L={L5} nf={nf5}\n    43→M6  vout   vbcp mid_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W6} L={L6} nf={nf6}\n    44→\n    45→* --- NMOS Cascode ---\n    46→M7  fold_p vbcn src_n7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W7} L={L7} nf={nf7}\n    47→M8  vout   vbcn src_n8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W8} L={L8} nf={nf8}\n    48→\n    49→* --- NMOS Current Source ---\n    50→M9  src_n7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W9} L={L9} nf={nf9}\n    51→M10 src_n8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W10} L={L10} nf={nf10}\n    52→\n    53→.ends ota_foldcasc\n    54→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01EZLvWR7y8upt6isXr71TxJ","session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"20422347-2d2a-44bd-9ad4-506762b71550","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:01:12.748Z"}
