{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TPeYsaKBCobsDyru8AX1xG","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→* ============================================================\n     2→* TB07: Operating Point Verification — VibroSense OTA\n     3→* Unity-gain feedback to establish mid-rail operating point\n     4→* ============================================================\n     5→\n     6→.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n     7→.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n     8→\n     9→.param vdd_val = 1.8\n    10→.param vcm_val = 0.9\n    11→\n    12→* Supply\n    13→Vdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\n    14→Vss vss 0 dc 0\n    15→\n    16→* Bias: diode-connected NMOS for Vbn (matches M11: W=4u L=4u)\n    17→Mbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\n    18→Ibias vdd vbn dc 500n\n    19→\n    20→* Vbcn: NMOS cascode bias (ideal source, tuned)\n    21→Vbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\n    22→\n    23→* Vbp: diode-connected PMOS (W=8u L=1u nf=2 matching M3)\n    24→Mbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\n    25→Ibp vbp 0 dc 500n\n    26→\n    27→* Vbcp: PMOS cascode bias (ideal source, tuned)\n    28→Vbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\n    29→\n    30→* Input at common-mode, OUTPUT FEEDS BACK TO INVERTING INPUT\n    31→Vinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val}\n    32→* Unity-gain feedback: vout -> vinn\n    33→* Use a large resistor to ensure DC feedback\n    34→Rfb vout vinn 1\n    35→\n    36→* Instantiate OTA\n    37→Xota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\n    38→\n    39→* Load capacitor\n    40→CL vout 0 10p\n    41→\n    42→.op\n    43→.save all\n    44→\n    45→.control\n    46→  run\n    47→\n    48→  echo \"\"\n    49→  echo \"======================================================\"\n    50→  echo \"  OPERATING POINT (Unity-Gain Feedback)\"\n    51→  echo \"======================================================\"\n    52→\n    53→  echo \"--- Bias Voltages ---\"\n    54→  print v(vbn) v(vbcn) v(vbp) v(vbcp) v(vout) v(vinp) v(vinn)\n    55→\n    56→  echo \"--- M1 (NMOS input +) ---\"\n    57→  print @m.xota.m1[id] @m.xota.m1[vgs] @m.xota.m1[vth] @m.xota.m1[vds] @m.xota.m1[vdsat] @m.xota.m1[gm] @m.xota.m1[gds]\n    58→\n    59→  echo \"--- M2 (NMOS input -) ---\"\n    60→  print @m.xota.m2[id] @m.xota.m2[vgs] @m.xota.m2[vth] @m.xota.m2[vds] @m.xota.m2[vdsat] @m.xota.m2[gm] @m.xota.m2[gds]\n    61→\n    62→  echo \"--- M3 (PMOS fold +) ---\"\n    63→  print @m.xota.m3[id] @m.xota.m3[vgs] @m.xota.m3[vth] @m.xota.m3[vds] @m.xota.m3[vdsat] @m.xota.m3[gm] @m.xota.m3[gds]\n    64→\n    65→  echo \"--- M4 (PMOS fold -) ---\"\n    66→  print @m.xota.m4[id] @m.xota.m4[vgs] @m.xota.m4[vth] @m.xota.m4[vds] @m.xota.m4[vdsat] @m.xota.m4[gm] @m.xota.m4[gds]\n    67→\n    68→  echo \"--- M5 (PMOS cascode +) ---\"\n    69→  print @m.xota.m5[id] @m.xota.m5[vgs] @m.xota.m5[vth] @m.xota.m5[vds] @m.xota.m5[vdsat] @m.xota.m5[gm] @m.xota.m5[gds]\n    70→\n    71→  echo \"--- M6 (PMOS cascode -) ---\"\n    72→  print @m.xota.m6[id] @m.xota.m6[vgs] @m.xota.m6[vth] @m.xota.m6[vds] @m.xota.m6[vdsat] @m.xota.m6[gm] @m.xota.m6[gds]\n    73→\n    74→  echo \"--- M7 (NMOS cascode +) ---\"\n    75→  print @m.xota.m7[id] @m.xota.m7[vgs] @m.xota.m7[vth] @m.xota.m7[vds] @m.xota.m7[vdsat] @m.xota.m7[gm] @m.xota.m7[gds]\n    76→\n    77→  echo \"--- M8 (NMOS cascode -) ---\"\n    78→  print @m.xota.m8[id] @m.xota.m8[vgs] @m.xota.m8[vth] @m.xota.m8[vds] @m.xota.m8[vdsat] @m.xota.m8[gm] @m.xota.m8[gds]\n    79→\n    80→  echo \"--- M9 (NMOS current src +) ---\"\n    81→  print @m.xota.m9[id] @m.xota.m9[vgs] @m.xota.m9[vth] @m.xota.m9[vds] @m.xota.m9[vdsat] @m.xota.m9[gm] @m.xota.m9[gds]\n    82→\n    83→  echo \"--- M10 (NMOS current src -) ---\"\n    84→  print @m.xota.m10[id] @m.xota.m10[vgs] @m.xota.m10[vth] @m.xota.m10[vds] @m.xota.m10[vdsat] @m.xota.m10[gm] @m.xota.m10[gds]\n    85→\n    86→  echo \"--- M11 (NMOS tail) ---\"\n    87→  print @m.xota.m11[id] @m.xota.m11[vgs] @m.xota.m11[vth] @m.xota.m11[vds] @m.xota.m11[vdsat] @m.xota.m11[gm] @m.xota.m11[gds]\n    88→\n    89→  echo \"--- M12 (PMOS bias mirror +) ---\"\n    90→  print @m.xota.m12[id] @m.xota.m12[vgs] @m.xota.m12[vth] @m.xota.m12[vds] @m.xota.m12[vdsat] @m.xota.m12[gm] @m.xota.m12[gds]\n    91→\n    92→  echo \"--- M13 (PMOS bias mirror -) ---\"\n    93→  print @m.xota.m13[id] @m.xota.m13[vgs] @m.xota.m13[vth] @m.xota.m13[vds] @m.xota.m13[vdsat] @m.xota.m13[gm] @m.xota.m13[gds]\n    94→\n    95→  echo \"======================================================\"\n    96→\n    97→  echo \"\"\n    98→  echo \"--- Supply Current ---\"\n    99→  print -i(Vdd)\n   100→\n   101→  quit\n   102→.endc\n   103→\n   104→.end\n   105→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01EZLvWR7y8upt6isXr71TxJ","session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"4fc62b8f-f66f-41ac-9085-26355562423b","timestamp":"2026-03-22T23:01:38.661Z"}
