.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc 1.8\nVss vss 0 dc 0\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc 500n\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\n\n* Same config as AC testbench: Vcm + AC source on vinp, inductor feedback\nVcm cm 0 dc 0.9\nVac vinp cm dc 0 ac 1\n\n* DC feedback via inductor (same as tb_ota_ac.spice)\nLfb vout vinn 1T\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n* Noise analysis: output-referred noise at vout, input source Vac\n* dec 100 points/decade, 1Hz to 1MHz\n.noise V(vout) Vac dec 100 1 1Meg\n\n.control\n  run\n\n  * Print input-referred noise spectrum at key frequencies\n  meas noise inoise_1k   FIND inoise_spectrum AT=1000\n  meas noise inoise_10k  FIND inoise_spectrum AT=10000\n  meas noise onoise_1k   FIND onoise_spectrum AT=1000\n  meas noise onoise_10k  FIND onoise_spectrum AT=10000\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n  echo \"  Noise Analysis Results\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n  echo \"Input-referred noise density:\"\n  echo \"  1 kHz:  $&inoise_1k  V/sqrt(Hz)\"\n  echo \"  10 kHz: $&inoise_10k V/sqrt(Hz)\"\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"Output-referred noise density:\"\n  echo \"  1 kHz:  $&onoise_1k  V/sqrt(Hz)\"\n  echo \"  10 kHz: $&onoise_10k V/sqrt(Hz)\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n\n  wrdata noise_data inoise_spectrum onoise_spectrum\n  quit\n.endc\n.end\n"}}
